Blocks.Text: That it wouldn't be her fault at all. that
she was a lady who, like her uncle Charla,
toch the highest pride in keeping her word. "/
could see 3amueler 3t'ing," he went on in a
lower voice, his sunker black eyes twinklig.
We all know how Balicon Island dangerous
to all Kial or Soats, wid d'ose big, big
roors in an' out ol de water.
